lead_paragraph: Olympic swimming star Michael Phelps, unbeknownst to the world, competed at the 2016 Summer Games in Brazil as a married man, having quietly wed his fiancée, former Miss California Nicole Johnson, weeks earlier, court records made public on Thursday showed.

headline.main: Olympic Swimming Star Michael Phelps Gets Married: Newspaper
